      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i know, i read the little warning on the bottle. but like, i'm not an idiot lol. i just really need to know if it's actually dangerous to take just one more dose of ibuprofen or if that's just what the labels always say to be safe. i've taken high doses before for migraines and i was fine. if i just take an extra 400mg it's not like i'm gonna die right, right? i just can't deal with this pain tonight.",
